---
import { arteImperceptibleBook } from "../data/featured";
import { contentShell } from "../config/layout";
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="scroll-mt-28 border-t border-stone-800/95 bg-[#151312]"
  aria-labelledby="about-heading"
>
  <div class:list={[contentShell, "py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20"]}>
    <h2 id="about-heading" class="font-display text-[1.875rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#fcf6ee]">
      About
    </h2>
    <div
      class="mt-8 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-x-12 lg:gap-y-10 xl:gap-x-16"
    >
      <div class="min-w-0 space-y-5 text-[0.9625rem] leading-[1.75] text-stone-400 lg:col-span-7">
        <p>
          I&apos;m a data scientist and software engineer focused on predictive modelling and recruiting analytics in football.
          I care about artefacts that survive hand-off: reproducible notebooks, observable services, dashboards that scouts
          revisit without needing a fresh onboarding every Monday.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most of my workload sits between{" "}
          <strong class="font-semibold text-stone-200">Levante UD</strong>{" "}(research collaborator on similarity-heavy scouting) and{" "}
          <strong class="font-semibold text-stone-200">Fever</strong>, where I ship Python services and ingestion at sustained traffic —
          Postgres tuning included.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p>
            Off the codebase: placing second at the{" "}
            <strong class="font-semibold text-stone-200">Aigües de Barcelona Data Challenge</strong>{" "}and credited participation
            alongside Levante in Alejandro Losa Brito&apos;s{" "}
            <a
              class="font-semibold italic text-amber-200 underline decoration-amber-500/55 underline-offset-[3px] transition hover:text-amber-50"
              href={arteImperceptibleBook.amazonUrl}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              {arteImperceptibleBook.titleShort}</a>.
          </p>
          <p class="rounded-md border border-stone-700/95 bg-[#141210]/90 px-[0.875rem] py-[0.6875rem] font-sans text-[0.85rem] leading-relaxed text-stone-500">
            Scout-facing book on imperceptible detail in modern football —
            paperback in Spanish (<span lang="es">scouting · match breakdown · club workflows</span>), released April&nbsp;2026.
            Listing:{" "}
            <a
              class="font-semibold text-amber-200 underline decoration-amber-500/55 underline-offset-[3px] hover:text-[#fff7ed]"
              href={arteImperceptibleBook.amazonUrl}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              Amazon.es&nbsp;<span aria-hidden="true">·</span> ISBN&nbsp;979-1387868925
            </a>
            <span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;(↗)</span>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="surface-muted rounded-lg p-6 lg:sticky lg:top-28 lg:col-span-5 lg:self-start xl:top-32" aria-label="Education snapshot">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-stone-500">Education</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[0.905rem] leading-relaxed text-stone-400">
          B.Sc. Computer Engineering (specialisation in data science),{" "}
          <strong class="font-medium text-stone-200">Universitat Pompeu Fabra · 2021–2025</strong>
          — thesis graded <strong class="font-medium text-stone-300">Excellent with Honours</strong>, same lineage as{" "}
          <em class="text-stone-300">Stars of the Future</em> listed in Projects.
        </p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
